title: 14-Gauge Square Point Shovel with American Ash Long Handle
description: The Bully Tools Square Point Shovel features a closed back, support rib for strength. Blade measures 11.75 in. x 9.5 in. with a 46.5 in. handle. Tool measures 56.75 in. long. The Bully Tools Square Point Shovel comes with a limited lifetime warranty that protects against defects in material and workmanship. Founded in 1994.
